Fix `cmake/aicxx/scripts/generate_libcwd_override.sh` so its debug-channel discovery remains compatible with both libcwd version 1 `channel_ct` declarations and the modern `Channel` declarations, and so it applies the channel declaration pattern only to lines between `NAMESPACE_DEBUG_CHANNELS_START` and `NAMESPACE_DEBUG_CHANNELS_END`. For example, only declarations inside such a marker block, such as `channel_ct endofmsg("ENDOFMSG");`, should contribute generated override channels.
